When you love and laugh abundantly, you live a beautiful life.
_

While traveling it's not always perfect like what you see in the pictures. There's long waits for buses, missed flights, lost luggage, miscommunications, and everything else under the sun, but the one thing that Megan and I have in common is that we both can laugh off any bad situation.
_

There's no situation in your life that you haven't survived thus far, so remember to laugh, because a smile is a curve that sets everything straight!
